<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Antipholus" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Antipholus,</orth> name of the twin brothers in <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.112" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 112</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 2</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.8" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.3.45" default="NO" valid="yes">3, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 5.13.45" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 13</bibl> etc. Plur. <emph>Antipholuses</emph> after the writing of M. Edd.; O. Edd. <emph>Antipholus,</emph> as it is required by the metre: <bibl n="shak. err 5.357.45" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 357</bibl>.
